                        <h3>9. 마라훠궈 (馬辣頂級麻辣鴛鴦火鍋)</h3>
                        <div class="restaurant-info">
                            <p><span class="info-label">시먼점 주소:</span> 108 대만 Taipei City, Wanhua District, Xining Rd, 157號2f <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=157+Xining+Rd,+2F,+Wanhua+District,+Taipei+City,+Taiwan+108" target="_blank" class="map-link">(지도 보기)</a></p>
                            <p><span class="info-label">시먼점 영업시간:</span> 11:30 ~ 02:00</p>
                            <p><span class="info-label">신의점 주소:</span> 110 대만 Taipei City, Xinyi District, Songshou Rd, 22號3樓 <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=22+Songshou+Rd,+3F,+Xinyi+District,+Taipei+City,+Taiwan+110" target="_blank" class="map-link">(지도 보기)</a></p>
