                            <p><span class="info-label">시먼점 영업시간:</span> 11:30 ~ 04:00</p>
                            <p><span class="info-label">다안점 주소:</span> No. 85號, Yanji St, Da'an District, Taipei City, 대만 106 <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=No.+85,+Yanji+St,+Da'an+District,+Taipei+City,+106+Taiwan" target="_blank" class="map-link">(지도 보기)</a></p>
