                        <h3>11. 하이디라오 (海底撈火鍋)</h3>
                        <div class="restaurant-info">
                            <p><span class="info-label">시먼점 주소:</span> 108412 대만 Taipei City, Wanhua District, Guilin Rd, 1號4樓 <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=1+Guilin+Rd,+4F,+Wanhua+District,+Taipei+City,+Taiwan+108412" target="_blank" class="map-link">(지도 보기)</a></p>
                            <p><span class="info-label">영업시간:</span> 11:00 ~ 03:00</p>
