                            <p><span class="info-label">은하동 주소:</span> No. 7, No. 7號, Longchang St, Wanhua District, Taipei City, 대만 108 <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=No.+7,+Longchang+St,+Wanhua+District,+Taipei+City,+108+Taiwan" target="_blank" class="map-link">(지도 보기)</a></p>
